71
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,360
His Majesty?

72
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,520
It's actually the Emperor?

73
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,520
Father.

74
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:13,960
Today,

75
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:15,600
the Prime Minister and I come together

76
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,520
to discuss important matters with you.

77
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,240
Where have you been?

78
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,680
Why the long delay?

79
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,160
I...

80
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,480
I was investigating something.

81
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,840
Regarding the imperial exam fraud

82
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:29,480
you mentioned earlier in court...

83
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:30,920
Father,

84
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,800
I have a more urgent matter.

85
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,880
The Prime Minister is here.

86
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:40,560
Other matters can wait.

87
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,280
This concerns the Crown Princess

88
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,680
and also her father,

89
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:46,120
the Prime Minister.

90
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:53,440
Qiu Yi.

91
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:54,760
Let me ask you.

92
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:56,920
Who is the father of the baby

93
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,160
in your womb?

94
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,640
What do you mean?

95
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:00,960
Could it be

96
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,680
that you suspect me?

97
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,520
(Diaries)
The diaries record

98
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,920
we never shared a bed after our wedding.

99
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,320
May I ask how you became pregnant?

100
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,840
Perhaps the diaries

101
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,440
merely omitted it.

102
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:14,400
Oh?

103
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,440
The diaries record

104
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,120
that after our wedding,

105
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,560
I kept traveling outside

106
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,640
and rarely returned.

107
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,280
Shall we get an imperial physician

108
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,320
to date your conception

109
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,440
and see if I was in the palace that day?

110
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,000
Someone.

111
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,160
Go get a physician.

112
00:06:36,720 --> 00:06:37,280
Enough.

113
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:38,720
Father.

114
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:39,920
I said enough!

115
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,720
The diaries

116
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,800
were recorded incorrectly.

117
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,160
That should be the case.

118
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,200
Father.

119
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,920
But the Crown Prince

120
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:50,960
harbors doubts.

121
00:06:51,640 --> 00:06:53,520
The child in the Crown Princess' womb

122
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,200
cannot be kept.

123
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:57,320
Your Majesty!

124
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,440
The Crown Princess

125
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,240
