her family home for so long.

126
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,080
Prime Minister,

127
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,320
you know what to do, correct?

128
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,120
Yes, Your Majesty.

129
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,760
Your Majesty,

130
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:19,080
I have an important matter to report.

131
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:21,240
What is it now?

132
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,000
I have investigated

133
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,520
the woman the Crown Prince married

134
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,760
in the countryside.

135
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,040
She is the daughter

136
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:32,000
of Shen Jinyuan, the criminal minister

137
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,200
who was executed
along with his entire family back then.

138
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,200
Is this true?

139
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,800
Father.

140
00:07:40,280 --> 00:07:41,480
The Shen family was framed.

141
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,440
Please clear Mr. Shen's name.

142
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,280
Your Highness.

143
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,920
It seems you truly have amnesia.

144
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:48,600
Do not forget that back then,

145
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,600
the one who issued the edict
to execute the entire Shen family

146
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,640
was none other than His Majesty!

147
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,440
The remnants of the Shen family

148
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,360
naturally

149
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,360
