150
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:05,520
Father.

151
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,040
Father.

152
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,040
Please see clearly.

153
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,520
The Shen family was truly framed.

154
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:12,520
Remember.

155
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,440
You were born into the imperial family.

156
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:17,200
Prioritize the greater good
in all matters.

157
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,760
Is this "greater good"

158
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,720
worth the truth?

159
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,480
How dare you!

160
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:33,240
From today, the Crown Prince
is confined to his palace.

161
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,920
Without my decree,

162
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,400
