163
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,080
Father.

164
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,000
Father.

165
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:40,720
Let go!

166
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:41,520
Father.

167
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:43,120
Father, please see clearly!

168
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,760
Let go! Let go!

169
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,920
Father.

170
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,600
Enough.

171
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,440
Your Highness.

172
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,560
A daughter of a disgraced official

173
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:56,160
raised in the countryside.

174
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:57,720
Killing her

175
00:08:58,520 --> 00:09:00,120
is of no consequence.

176
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,600
Father.

177
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,400
Father, please see clearly.

178
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,400
Why?

179
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:24,400
Why are you the son
of my father's killer?

